request.description:
Uploads an image to IPFS via BasedBid CDN.

**Field name**: `file` (multipart formdata)

**Success response**:
```json
{
  "ok": true,
  "response": { "cid": "...", "url": "https://ipfs.based.bid/ipfs/..." }
}
```

Use `response.url` as `logoUrl` or `bannerUrl` in subsequent requests.
